.SH "BUILDING XQ\-API"
.sp
To build xq\-api, you can use make:
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
$ make xq\-api
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
And to build the manpage:
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
$ make xq\-api.8
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
Or, to build both:
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
$ make
.fi
.if n .RE
.sp
Otherwise, to build xq\-api with the Go tool from within the source tree:
.sp
.if n .RS 4
.nf
$ go build go.spiff.io/xq\-api
.fi
